name: Q&A and a look towards 2019
description:
This channel started as a  hobby and I never dreamed it would ever grow to what it has become.  Along the way I have been overwhelmed by the encouragement and positive messaged from the YouTube and aviation world.  I have also received many questions - this video tries to answer as many of those as possible. 

Thank you too everybody who has watched, liked and commented on my videos - your support is greatly appreciated and is very humbling.

Happy travels and a safe, happy and healthy 2019 to all. 

Cheers

Dennis
